<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Withings API Connect</h1>
    <p class="lead">Welcome to the Withings API App. Making it easier for you to access Withings data. </p>
    <p><a href="http://localhost:49932/Withings/Authorize" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started! &raquo;</a></p>
